reviewText: Shaoran's group is stuck in the magic library. Each of the travelers must face a trial and discover their true self. Even Mokona must answer the call for a hero. While Sakura is stuck in a world that makes her think of home, her memories of Shaoran are not restored. We all know that that is the price for saving her life, but it's still a very sad thing to see happen. At least they can make new memories together.
